no-loop ruleflow-group "assign-bed" when $pI: WorkflowProcessInstanceImpl( variables['bedrequest_entity'] == "911") $hospital: Hospital(availableBeds > 0) then $hospital.setAvailableBeds($hospital.getAvailableBeds()-1); update($hospital);

no-loop ruleflow-group "assign-bed" when $hospital: Hospital(availableBeds > 0) $bedService: BedService() $bedRequest: BedRequest(requestingEntity == "911", patientAge > 20 , assignedBed == 0 ) then int assignedBed = $bedService.requestBed("ER"); $bedRequest.setAssignedBed(assignedBed); update($bedRequest);

no-loop ruleflow-group "assign-bed" when $hospital: Hospital(availableBeds > 0) $bedService: BedService() $bedRequest: BedRequest(requestingEntity == "911", patientAge < 20, assignedBed == 0 ) then int assignedBed = $bedService.requestBed("ER"); $bedRequest.setAssignedBed(assignedBed); update($bedRequest);

sv:property.sv:value: no-loop salience 2 ruleflow-group "assign-bed" when $hospital: Hospital(availableBeds > 0) $bedService: BedService() $bedRequest: BedRequest(requestingEntity == "911", patientAge > 20 , patientStatus == "heart attack", assignedBed == 0 ) then int assignedBed = $bedService.requestBed("Intensive Care"); $bedRequest.setAssignedBed(assignedBed); update($bedRequest);
